Package it.polimi.ingsw.PSP48.networkMessagesToClient

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChallengerDivinitiesSelectionRequest
    Network message used to request the challenger to choose the available divinities in the game.
    ChangedBoard
    Network message that triggers an update board on the client, when on server some cells changed their content.
    DivinitySelectionRequest
    Network message used to request the player to choose his divinity.
    EndGameMessage
    Network message that notifies the client that the game ended.
    InitialPlayerRequestMessage
    A network message sent to the client to requests the selection of the first player to the challenger.
    NetworkMessagesToClient
    A network message to the client.
    OptionalMoveRequest
    Network messages sent to client to request the player to complete an optional move action, or to skip it.
    PositioningRequest
    Network message to requests the player to put a worker on the game board
    RequestBuild
    Network messages sent to client to request the player to complete an optional build action, or to skip it.
    RequestMessagePrint
    Network messages that requests the client to show at video a message.
    RequestMove
    Network messages sent to client to request the player to complete a move action.
    RequestOpionalBuild
    Network messages sent to client to request the player to complete an optional build action, or to skip it.
    UpdatedPlayerList
    Messages containing a new player-divinity association list
